{
 "name": "RPlog_Orson_the_Artist",
 "title": "Orson the Artist",
 "summary": "In the cleared area before the main house at Karrde's base on Myrkr, the mechanic Orson reveals an unexpected artistic side to the Jedi Jessalyn Valios. Setting aside his tools, the gruff, practical man turns his creative energies toward making something for its own sake, surprising his companion with a softer, more expressive dimension of his character. Jessalyn watches with warmth and quiet delight as Orson works. The scene paints a tender portrait of the unlikely artist and the bond he shares with his Jedi teacher.",
